ackground:none !important;\">\r\n							<tbody>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td class=\"number\" style=\"font-size:10pt !important;border:0px !important;vertical-align:top !important;font-family:Consolas, \'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono\', \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace !important;color:#AFAFAF !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n										3\r\n									</td>\r\n									<td class=\"content\" style=\"font-size:10pt !important;vertical-align:top !important;font-family:Consolas, \'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono\', \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n										return&nbsp;\"Hello!\";\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n							</tbody>\r\n						</table>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"line alt2\" style=\"padding:0px !important;margin:0px !important;border:0px !important;vertical-align:baseline !important;font-size:10pt !important;background:none #F8F8F8 !important;\">\r\n						<table style=\"font-size:10pt !important;margin:0px !important;padding:0px !important;border:0px !important;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n							<tbody>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td class=\"number\" style=\"font-size:10pt !important;border:0px !important;vertical-align:top !important;font-family:Consolas, \'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono\', \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace !important;color:#AFAFAF !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n										4\r\n									</td>\r\n									<td class=\"content\" style=\"font-size:10pt !important;vertical-align:top !important;font-family:Consolas, \'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono\', \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n										}\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n							</tbody>\r\n						</table>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"line alt1\" style=\"padding:0px !important;margin:0px !important;border:0px !important;vertical-align:baseline !important;font-size:10pt !important;\">\r\n						<table style=\"font-size:10pt !important;margin:0px !important;padding:0px !important;border:0px !important;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n							<tbody>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td class=\"number\" style=\"font-size:10pt !important;border:0px !important;vertical-align:top !important;font-family:Consolas, \'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono\', \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace !important;color:#AFAFAF !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n										5\r\n									</td>\r\n									<td class=\"content\" style=\"font-size:10pt !important;vertical-align:top !important;font-family:Consolas, \'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono\', \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n										})-&gt;myMethod();\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n							</tbody>\r\n						</table>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"line alt2\" style=\"padding:0px !important;margin:0px !important;border:0px !important;vertical-align:baseline !important;font-size:10pt !important;background:none #F8F8F8 !important;\">\r\n						<table style=\"font-size:10pt !important;margin:0px !important;padding:0px !important;border:0px !important;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n							<tbody>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td class=\"number\" style=\"font-size:10pt !important;border:0px !important;vertical-align:top !important;font-family:Consolas, \'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono\', \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace !important;color:#AFAFAF !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n										6\r\n									</td>\r\n									<td class=\"content\" style=\"font-size:10pt !important;vertical-align:top !important;font-family:Consolas, \'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono\', \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n										//Result: Hello!\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n							</tbody>\r\n						</table>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n<h4 microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" stheiti,=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" simsun,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" lucida,=\"\" verdana,=\"\" serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0.5px;=\"\" background:=\"\" rgb(238,=\"\" 245,=\"\" 251);\"=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Lucida Grande\', \'Lucida Sans Unicode\', Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4. 更多Error错误可以进行异常处理\r\n			</h4>\r\n<p microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" stheiti,=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" simsun,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" lucida,=\"\" verdana,=\"\" serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0.5px;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" 32px;\"=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Lucida Grande\', \'Lucida Sans Unicode\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PHP7中更多的Error变为可捕获的Exception返回给开发者，如果不进行捕获则为Error，如果捕获就变为一个可在程序内处理的 Exception。默认情况下，Error会直接导致程序中断，而PHP7则通过try / catch程序块捕获并且处理，让程序继续执行下去，为程序员提供更灵活的选择。\r\n				</p>\r\n<p microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" stheiti,=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" simsun,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" lucida,=\"\" verdana,=\"\" serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0.5px;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" 32px;\"=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Lucida Grande\', \'Lucida Sans Unicode\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">代码示例：\r\n			</p>\r\n			<div style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;color:#666666;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Lucida Grande\', \'Lucida Sans Unicode\', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n				<div id=\"highlighter_420676\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter \" style=\"padding:1px !important;margin:1em 0px !important;border:0px !important;vertical-align:baseline !important;font-family:Consolas, \'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono\', \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace !important;font-size:10pt !important;\">\r\n					<div class=\"lines\" style=\"padding:0px !important;margin:0px !important;border:0px !important;vertical-align:baseline !important;font-size:10pt !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n						<div class=\"line alt1\" style=\"padding:0px !important;margin:0px !important;border:0px !important;vertical-align:baseline !important;font-size:10pt !important;\">\r\n							<table style=\"font-size:10pt !important;margin:0px !important;padding:0px !important;border:0px !important;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n								<tbody>\r\n									<tr>\r\n										<td class=\"number\" style=\"font-size:10pt !important;border:0px !important;vertical-align:top !important;font-family:Consolas, \'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono\', \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace !important;color:#AFAFAF !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n											1\r\n										</td>\r\n										<td class=\"content\" style=\"font-size:10pt !important;vertical-align:top !important;font-family:Consolas, \'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono\', \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace !important;background:none !important;\">\r\n											nonExistFunction($arg);&nbsp;// It will generate fatal error\r\n										</td>\r\n									</tr>\r\n								</tbody>\r\n							</table>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n<p microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" stheiti,=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" simsun,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" lucida,=\"\" verdana,=\"\" serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0.5px;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" 32px;\"=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Lucida Grande\', \'Lucida Sans Unicode\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这时上面的代码会提示错误“Fatal error: Call to a member function method() on a non-object ”，并且这个致命错误会停止后面代码的继续执行。\r\n				</p>\r\n<p microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" stheiti,=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" simsun,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" lucida,=\"\" verdana,=\"\" serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0.5px;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" 32px;\"=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Lucida Grande\', \'Lucida Sans Unicode\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">所以如果你想继续执行代码，可以通过异常处理的方式解决：\r\n			</p>\r\n			<div style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;color:#666666;font-family:Arial, Verdana, 微软雅黑, \'Lucida Grande\', \'Lucida Sans Unicode\', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n				<div id=\"highlighter_146449\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter \" style=\"padding:1px !important;margin:1em 0px !important;border:0px !important;vertical-align:baseline !important;font-family:Consolas, \'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono\', \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace !important;font-size:10pt !important;\">\r\n					<div class=\"lines\" style=\"padding:0px !i